Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上一次升级系统是什么时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}When was the last time you did a system upgrade?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为自己这是在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道规矩的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Okay. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许...碰我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No... touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们玩得这些游戏...没一个起作用的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}All these games we play... none of them work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  许  碰  我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You do not lay hands on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前从没这么做过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You've never done this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能碰你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I can't touch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:02.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拥有世界上最大的IT公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I own the biggest IT company in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人都对我有所求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Everyone wants something from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人都想要我给予的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Everyone wants what I have to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我简直如同上帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's like I'm a fucking god.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我来这里  以求恢复一些平衡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So I come here to restore some balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我还以为你会和其他人不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Because I thought that you were different than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有人和我一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}There are no others like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很特别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You're special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  我  确实很特别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}As a matter of fact, I am special.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为我选择了和你共度良宵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Because I choose to spend my time with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No!
