Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由威廉·亨廷顿·桑德斯支付购买\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}bought and paid for by William Huntington Sanders.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你可以喊我比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But you can call me Bill.
