Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然知道你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I know exactly who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我会展示给你看的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But I will show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是你想要的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Is this what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是比奇丝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I am Bilquis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有美丽的源泉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Mother of all beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空因我而有色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I am the color of the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳因我而生光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I give light to the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}...are nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}机密  本人亲启
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}科里亚达节\N卓娅·维切恩亚亚家人邀请您一起追思\N我们的晚间之星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最亲爱的影子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}My dearest Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须谈谈你的头脑和内心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We must speak of your head and your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}邀请您来悼念我们的晚间之星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽快前来  卓娅·维切恩亚亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Please attend. Urgently, Zorya Polunochnaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  别忘了带上硬币\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Also, don't forget to bring the coin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上  迈克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}For heaven's sake, Mike,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你体温过低前快上车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}get in the car before you get hypothermia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这样的天气下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}In weather like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿着不合适的衣服在外面待了五分钟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}you're out there for five minutes with improper attire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.66,0:14:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会儿你唯一能搭的车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and well, the only ride you're gonna need
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是去欧克莱尔验尸官那里的车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}is to the coroner's in Eau Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.69,0:14:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正要进城买件外套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I was walking into town to buy a jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好你长得帅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's a good thing you're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这辆漂亮的老古董\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Ah! Look at the beautiful clunker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老古董\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Clunker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年  我们找一辆报废的车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Every year, we take a wreck,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它放在湖面上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}we put it out on the lake,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  大家会猜测春天将至时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and then, folks guess the date and the time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废车压破冰面的日期和时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}when it'll break through the ice come spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  获胜者和高中平分奖金\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And then, the winner splits the pot with the high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You're gonna love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}湖畔镇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:44.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然湖畔镇以渔业闻名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Now, while Lakeside is known for its fishing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}全美最棒的馅饼之乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但真正让我们出名的是好吃到死的馅饼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}it's the to-die-for pasties that put us on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}圣诞馅饼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一口都像温暖的拥抱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Every delicious bite is like a warm hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你知道这地方最特别的是什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But you know what really makes this place special?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:15:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里的每个人都真心关心他们的邻居\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Everyone here genuinely cares for their neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们一切行为的出发点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's in everything we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种精神是由本镇第一位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}This spirit was passed down to us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居民及资助人莱斯特·汉密尔顿传给我们的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}by the town's first citizen and benefactor, Lester Hamilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死后  将财产留给了湖畔镇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And when he died, he left Lakeside his fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是镇民才能继续繁荣昌盛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}so that its citizens would continue to prosper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只要求我们尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}All he asked in return was that we honor
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一些他最喜欢的旧世界传统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}some of his favorite Old World traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以每年我们都会举办一个冰雪节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So every year, we hold an ice festival
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.03,0:15:28.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来庆祝他的慷慨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}to celebrate his generosity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢我们神奇的小镇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and give thanks for our magical little town
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及此处的北欧传统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and its Nordic heritage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你会喜欢这里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I think you're gonna like it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可抗力鼠脸假蝇鱼钩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Rat-Faced Irresistible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦你有这些宝贝的消息传出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The trout'll jump into your frying pan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳟鱼都会自己跳进你的煎锅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}once word gets out you got one of these babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安玛莉  你要把这可怜人的耳朵都唠叨掉了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You talking this poor man's ear off, Ann-Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,李·亨宁斯  店主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Lee Hennings, proprietor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克·安塞尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Mike Ainsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:15:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗  安塞尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What can we do for you, Mr. Ainsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得给这家伙找件比运动衫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You need to get this fella into something warmer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更暖和的衣服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}than a sweatshirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用特别硬核的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Nothing too hardcore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道我会在这个地方待多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Not sure how long I'll be in this part of the country for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是戈尔曼街的新租客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}He's the new tenant on Gorman Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈尔曼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Gorman? Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还在想什么时候会有人搬进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We were wondering when somebody was gonna move in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉森  你能带安塞尔先生去看看大衣吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Alison, can you show Mr. Ainsel the parkas, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞节后  我们的毛衣也有大减价的活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And we've got some great after-Christmas sales on sweaters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Hey. I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.99,0:16:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚  在巴士外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Last night, outside of the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我朋友太胡闹了  我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}um, my friend and I were being jerks. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天过得很糟糕  让我开心一下吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I was having a bad day. Made me smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Um, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是大衣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Uh, well, here are the parkas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是打折的毛衣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And, um, here are the on-sale sweaters,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就我来说  我会避开圣诞节款式的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}although, personally, I'd avoid the Christmas ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们超级土的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}They're super lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.22,0:16:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Right. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这件怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Let's see what this one looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说  看起来很适合你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I mean... I mean it seems to fit you really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对我来说就够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, that is good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I will take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  来看毛衣  有驯鹿的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Right, these sweaters. Anything in reindeer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  有的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Uh, yeah, yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉森  我们卖安塞尔先生一张破车票怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What say we sell Mr. Ainsel a clunker ticket, Alison?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正想问呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I was just about to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.48,0:17:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.67,0:17:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需要选个日期和时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Just need to, uh, pick a date and a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得它什么时候会压穿冰层\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}When do you think it will go through the ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}三月  破车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3月23日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}March 23rd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上七点到八点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}7 p.m. till 8 p.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.34,0:17:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  大多数人都会多选几天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Okay. Uh, most people pick more than one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我猜这就是你的策略吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But, uh, I guess this is your strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.50,0:17:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我想我必须欣赏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Okay. Well, I guess I gotta admire
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个相信自己直觉的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}a man who goes with his instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好运  一共五美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Good luck. Five dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪颗牙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}which one of your teeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}are loose, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这颗吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Is it this one here? Ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么糟糕  不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Now that wasn't so bad, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么糟  你猜怎么着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No. Hey, I'll tell you what,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能让我留下这颗臼齿做研究\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'll pay you twice the Tooth Fairy's going rate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你牙仙两倍的价钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}if I may keep this molar for my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}泰瑞尔合作公司
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的士兵最早是什么时候带着图腾去战斗的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}When did our soldiers first carry our totems into battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古德弗雷德进攻法兰克但是搞砸了那时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}When Gudfred fucked up that Frankish business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上一次是约克镇战役\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The last time was Yorktown.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不再做黑森佣兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}We abandoned our post as Hessian Jaegers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后加入了华盛顿的军队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and joined Washington's ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争的艺术有一半是知道何时转移阵营\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Half the art of war is knowing when to switch sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你混得挺好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You have done well for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还挺舒适的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, I'm comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提尔  北欧战神  舒适\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Tyr, the warlord, comfortable?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角斗士的杀戮欲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, the gladiator's bloodlust
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖相不太好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}doesn't make for a very lucrative business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果你需要战神出场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Ha! But if it's a war god you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只需要你捐个款就行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}All I want from you is a donation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:56.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受宠若惊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}冬至暖愉\N爱你\N德墨忒尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大老远过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You came all this way
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本来可以在芝加哥见我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}when you could have put the touch on me in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科里亚达节\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}At the Koliada?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}科里亚达节\N卓娅·维切恩亚亚家人邀请您一起追思\N我们的晚间之星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芝加哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了卓娅·维切恩亚亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}For Zorya Vechernyaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能等到那个时候吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Couldn't wait 'til then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起诉战争是一个费时费力的差事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Prosecuting the war is an all-consuming endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有事情在最后一刻出现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Things come up all the time, last minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然追悼会是好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Memorials are all well and good,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们都知道以牙还牙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}but we both know that an eye for an eye
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不便宜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}don't come cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切为了事业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, anything for the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该署名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Should I make it out to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡什[现金]就好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}"Cash" Will be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真大方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Very generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.89,0:21:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(190,270)}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\i1\fsp1\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H7BE6FF&}我在你身边战斗  奥丁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2\pos(190,270)}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\i1\fsp1\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H7BE6FF&}战斗至死  或者杀死我们的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的牙怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}How are your teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想得美\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Nice try.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好啊  萨尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, top of the morning to you, Sal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.51,0:21:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我说到哪了  对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}All right, where was I? Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湖畔新闻社就在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Okay, Lakeside News is just down that-a-way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是扎克里·摩根在1902年创建的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It was started by Zachary Morgan in 1902.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他得了梅毒  穿着尿不湿死的  可怜的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}He died of syphilis wearing a diaper, poor fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错  其实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Nice. Um, so actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安迪  但愿你是在给你老婆买礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Andy! I hope you're looking for a present for your wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个的结婚纪念日马上到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Your anniversary is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.71,0:21:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他经常忘记一些事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}He happens to forget things
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像结婚纪念日这种  一年一次的婚姻事件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}like annual marital events, like anniversaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅宝家餐馆就在这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Mabel's Restaurant is right over here,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的馅饼  就像我之前说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and the pasties, as I mentioned earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直棒极了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}are the best things ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗  她传承了她奶奶的配方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You know, she inherited the recipe from her grandmother,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而她奶奶是从康沃尔郡带来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}who brought it over here from Cornwall.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能不能快速插一句\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}If I could just sneak in
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问一下我在哪里能租一辆车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}a quick question about where to rent a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你应该找欧克莱尔  那\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, that's Eau Claire, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从玛莎那里听说凯西的内衣被偷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I heard from Martha that Kathy's unmentionables were stolen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.38,0:22:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是直接从洗衣篮里偷的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}right from her laundry basket!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I know, I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先不要因为一点点谣言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Let's not all get in a fuss
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就大惊小怪的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}over the Piggly Wiggly rumor mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你好啊  安玛丽  -你好  柴德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- Oh, hey, Ann-Marie. - Hi, Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.49,0:22:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克  看起来李·亨宁斯把你照顾得挺好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, Mike. I see Lee Henning's taken good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你看起来更像本地人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Now you're lookin' more local.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.85,0:22:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少暖和了不少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Lot warmer at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅格·冈瑟在激动什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What's Meg Gunther in a lather about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.97,0:22:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内衣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Lingerie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.59,0:22:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然  她的一周一轮的内衣丢了三套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Apparently, three pairs of her days-of-the-week underwear:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.05,0:22:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期三的  星期四的和星期六的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Wednesday, Thursday, and Saturday,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全从烘干机里消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}all went missing from the dryer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她就认为  我们有一个  在逃内衣贼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So, in her mind, we have a, uh, panty thief on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  迈克  这就算得上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}See, Mike, this is what qualifies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湖畔镇的重罪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}as major crime here in Lakeside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.16,0:22:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俗话说得好  如果你有钱  你在蒙特卡洛生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You know, if you're rich, you live in Monte Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你出名  就住在加州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And if you're famous, you live in California.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.29,0:22:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果你很幸运  那你就住在这  湖畔镇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But if you're lucky, you live here in... in Lakeside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.95,0:23:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死  我要去水湾那里找巴特了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, shoot. I'm supposed to meet Bart up at the inlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太抱歉了  柴德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I am so sorry. Um, hey, Chad,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.85,0:23:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能带我们的新人去尝尝馅饼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}could you get our newest resident situated with a pasty?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不用再问我第二遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, you don't have to ask me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我要饿死了  -太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- I'm starving. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-来吧  -好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- Come on. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.40,0:23:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谢谢你  -你肯定会喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- Thank you. - You're gonna love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.24,0:23:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗  有趣的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You know, interestingly, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅宝的美味馅饼配方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Mabel's amazing pasty recipe,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.07,0:23:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实她是传承她奶奶的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}she actually inherited from her grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大老远从康沃尔郡来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Came all the way from Cornwall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Grab a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.56,0:23:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好啊  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}How you doing this morning, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅宝  这是迈克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Hey, Mabel, this is Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.32,0:23:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他住在戈尔曼街\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}He's staying up at the spot on Gorman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.97,0:23:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你  迈克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's nice to meet you, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看看菜单吗  亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Can I show you a menu, hon?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.58,0:23:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在说馅饼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, everyone's been talking about these pasties.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一份馅饼  店里赠送\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}One pasty on the house it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.53,0:23:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免费赠送给第一次光顾的顾客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's complimentary to first-time customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.01,0:23:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  能不能再来杯咖啡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Thank you. Can I get a coffee too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经知道这牛仔要吃什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I already know what this cowboy's having.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.59,0:23:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穆里根局长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Chief Mulligan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.80,0:23:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What's good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.02,0:23:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让我干等着  小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Don't leave me hanging, dawg.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识德瑞克吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You know Derek?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认识\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他只是想让我知道有他这么个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I think he just wants me to know he's down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是做什么工作的  迈克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So, what do you do for a living, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.81,0:24:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就替我叔叔干活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Just working for my uncle right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.48,0:24:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是做什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What's he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.73,0:24:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他做进出口贸易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}He runs an import-export business.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.63,0:24:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  哪一种\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Yeah? What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.41,0:24:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分都是古董\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Antiques, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.79,0:24:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我语气像警察问话  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I sound like a cop, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.78,0:24:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,习惯成自然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Yeah, that's a force of habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.02,0:24:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  迈克  对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Jeez, Mike, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.92,0:24:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不是故意要打听  -没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}- I don't mean to pry. - It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.91,0:24:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃的来了  先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Here you go, gents.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.94,0:24:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.42,0:24:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Now, careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.78,0:24:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你饿着肚子离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}If you leave here hungry,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.92,0:24:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你自己的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}it's your own dang fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.28,0:24:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.43,0:24:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心  这些会上瘾的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Careful. They're addictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.65,0:24:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也许知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You might know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.60,0:25:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有比欧克莱尔更近的租车地方吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Is there anywhere closer than Eau Claire to rent a car?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.08,0:25:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}「湖畔镇日报」\N新酒店开张
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.83,0:25:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}「湖畔镇日报」\N暴风雨后码头需要修葺
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.97,0:25:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.39,0:25:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看谁和我一起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Look who I got with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.02,0:25:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柴德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Hi, Chad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.86,0:25:17.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安塞尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Mr. Ainsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.61,0:25:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,房管小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Ms. Property Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.13,0:25:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说你们俩见过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So, you two have met.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.59,0:25:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在枪口下认识的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}At gun point.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.07,0:25:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安塞尔先生昨晚想闯进他的公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Mr. Ainsel tried to break into his apartment last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.15,0:25:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为钥匙不好使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Due to a key malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.00,0:25:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好没人受伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Fortunately, no one was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.60,0:25:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更明智的做法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, the wiser course of action
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.05,0:25:37.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是打电话给当地的执法部门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}would have been to call your local law enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.58,0:25:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}「湖畔镇日报」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.89,0:25:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迈克想找交通工具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Mike here is looking for some transportation,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.93,0:25:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到了桑迪的旧车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and, Sandy's old beater came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.22,0:25:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那辆车不卖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The car is not for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.28,0:25:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车子已经停在后面差不多两年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's... been parked out back better part of two years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.03,0:26:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜在紧急情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Possible 10-99.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.46,0:26:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从马里埃尔·拉森的福特福莱克斯车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Bag of laundry taken out
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.53,0:26:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了的洗衣店袋子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}of Mariel Larson's Ford Flex.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.67,0:26:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强盗又来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Bandit strikes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.82,0:26:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻赶过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}10-76.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.01,0:26:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp1\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}「湖畔镇日报」
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.12,0:26:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先声明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}For the record,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.31,0:26:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想租车\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I was only lookin' to rent the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.15,0:26:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想去芝加哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Just trying to get to Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.68,0:26:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要去芝加哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What's in Chicago?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.37,0:26:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加朋友的追悼会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Memorial service for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.44,0:26:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天下午就走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I leave this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.19,0:26:33.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你要等个一两天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You may want to wait a day or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.50,0:26:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴风雨过后州际公路总是一片混乱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The interstate's always a mess after a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.96,0:26:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我得去那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I need to be there tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.76,0:26:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但明天我就回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But I'll be back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.18,0:26:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两天一百美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}A hundred dollars for the two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.35,0:26:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把车完好无损地开回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Bring it back like you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.43,0:26:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我把车洗了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}If I get it cleaned up?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.99,0:26:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百五十美元\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}A hundred and fifty.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.22,0:26:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是唯一一把钥匙  别弄断了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}That's the only key. Try not to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.45,0:26:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.19,0:27:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真主至上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Allahu akbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.33,0:27:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会来开罗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What brings you back to Cairo?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.04,0:27:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我的新任务对星期三先生来说至关重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}"My new mission is of vital importance to Mr. Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.50,0:27:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道需要多长时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I don't know how long it will take
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.15,0:27:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是我会离开多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}or how long I will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.65,0:28:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当这是我们旅程的终点吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Consider this the end of our journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.27,0:28:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别找我"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Don't look for me."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.72,0:28:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你对这个"任务"一无所知吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}So you know nothing of this "Mission"?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.34,0:28:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经好几月没见到星期三先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I haven't seen or heard anything
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.75,0:28:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有他的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}from Mr. Wednesday in months.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.76,0:28:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}All I know is whatever task
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.47,0:28:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星期三给精灵指派的任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Wednesday has demanded of the Jinn,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.21,0:28:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们从此分离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}it has driven us apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.22,0:28:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也许是精灵自己决定的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But perhaps the Jinn made up his own mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.72,0:28:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉会变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Feelings can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.72,0:28:36.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他真的不爱我了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}If he truly does not love me,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.59,0:28:39.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要听他当面告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I need to hear him say it to my face.
