Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.66,0:30:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.37,0:30:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一顿都在不断变差\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Every meal worse than the last.
