Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.97,0:31:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的朋友们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}My friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.87,0:31:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬我们最爱的卓娅·维切恩亚亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}To our beloved Zorya Vechernyaya.
