Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.54,0:31:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}What the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.13,0:31:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你怎么来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I said, what the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.67,0:31:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去  没邀请你来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Out. You were not invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.88,0:31:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没邀请我  可我还是来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Neither was I! But here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.31,0:31:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.39,0:31:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有晚间之星的引导\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Without our evening star to guide us,
