Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.80,0:32:05.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是应该在湖畔镇吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Shouldn't you be in Lakeside?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.61,0:32:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是位非常特别的女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Look, she was a special lady.
