Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.13,0:32:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礼物放在那边的桌子上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Gifts go over there to table.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.68,0:32:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我带来了...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Yeah, I brought, I brought...
