Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.53,0:32:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,节哀顺变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I'm sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.05,0:32:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Very well done.
