Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.42,0:32:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子进步了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The kid's learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.33,0:32:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你遗忘了最重要的部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}But, you missed the most important bit of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.51,0:32:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出自丹麦首都大区最棒的芝士工厂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}From the finest cheese laboratory in Hovedstaden,
