Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.82,0:32:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一份心意帮你暂时逃离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}a token that you may temporarily escape
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.54,0:32:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去姐妹的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}the agony of losing a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.96,0:32:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个冷血性感的贱人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}She was a cold-hearted, sexy bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.57,0:32:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为什么喜欢你  我一点也不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And why she liked you, I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.48,0:32:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}It's beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.73,0:32:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你  我想我们还有事没完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}And you, I think we have some unfinished business.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.90,0:33:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不在乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I don't care
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.10,0:33:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会不会护住你那漂亮的头骨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}if you try to cover that nice skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.37,0:33:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的锤子与它的约定尚在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}My hammer still has an appointment with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.76,0:33:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以肯定这不是邀请我来的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Pretty sure that's not why I was invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.48,0:33:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没邀请你来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You were not invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.21,0:33:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人名单上绝对有我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Well, definitely on the guest list.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.55,0:33:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这字真漂亮  失传的艺术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Outstanding calligraphy. It's a lost art.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.10,0:33:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妹妹邀请了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Your sister invited him.
