Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.40,0:33:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一同回忆卓娅·维切恩亚亚的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and remember the wisdom and beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.47,0:33:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智慧与美丽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}of Zorya Vechernyaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.02,0:33:46.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许你提她的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Hey, you take that name out of your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.00,0:33:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这些的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Oh, this is not the place or the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.53,0:33:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃坦  听好了  这是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Votan! Listen, you did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.08,0:33:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你基本上等同于扣下了扳机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}You as good as pulled the trigger of the gun
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.37,0:33:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了她的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}that ended her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.18,0:33:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是被共同的敌人谋杀的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}She was murdered by shared enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.98,0:33:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好大的胆子  沃坦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}The balls on you, Votan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.72,0:34:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是来向卓娅致敬的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Are you here to pay your respect to Zorya?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.05,0:34:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不是  你来是为了你那愚蠢的战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I don't think so. You're here because of your stupid war.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.64,0:34:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是罪过吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Is that a sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.44,0:34:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这里是为了悼念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I came here to mourn the death
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.12,0:34:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾心爱之人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}of someone who once owned my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.93,0:34:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时发现自己周围站满了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}and at the same time find myself surrounded
