Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.39,0:34:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说  你忘了我们的事业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Or... have you forgotten our cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.33,0:34:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是忘记了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Has it slipped your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.82,0:34:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  岑诺伯格  夜神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}that you, Czernobog, the Dark One,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.88,0:34:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾发誓效忠于我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}swore an oath to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.57,0:34:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬晚间之星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}To the evening star.
