Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.12,0:35:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走到哪里都带着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}I carry it everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.33,0:35:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你和它一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Because you are just like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.72,0:35:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是一半在光明  一半在黑暗之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14\c&H4bc2ef&}Always half in light, half in shadow.
